simplehttpd - simple HTTP daemon
================================

USAGE

    simplehttpd [-Cv] [-c config] [-d docroot] [-l addr] [-p port]

OPTIONS

    -c path     use an alternate config file
    -d path     use alternate docroot (overrides config)
    -h          display usage message
    -l address  listen on specified address (overrides config)
    -p port     listen on specified port (overrides config)
    -v          display version message

FILES

    simplehttpd.conf
        Default configuration file.

    ~/public_html
        Default docroot

